<p><a id="TSJN-01-04-0807-kw-9901" class="keywordref" title="jump to Your letter in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0807-ks-9901">Your letter</a>: Banisters undated letter printed above under 15? Feb., q.v. Banister was paid on 17 Mch. (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Council of the State of Virginia&lt;/i&gt;, ed. H. R. McIlwaine ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Va. Council Jour</span>.</span>, <span class="hi-small-caps" style="font-variant: small-caps;">ii</span>, 311).</p></div>
